《'''黑白无双'''》，原名'''黑白无常'''，是责编小狐与设计者WINFIELD，作者[[于彦舒|于彦舒]]画的漫画。获得金龙奖第2届最佳故事漫画奖。两主角小黑小白是鬼差。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://tjgame.enorth.com.cn/system/2007/05/22/001673082.shtml|title=《黑白无双》单行本面市|language=zh-cn|publisher=北方网|author=王铮|date=2007-05-22|accessdate=2015-04-23|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304074604/http://tjgame.enorth.com.cn/system/2007/05/22/001673082.shtml|archivedate=2016-03-04|df=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://game.21cn.com/comic/news/a/2007/0419/15/3188817.shtml|title=少年心性《黑白无双》单行本登场|language=zh-cn|publisher=21cn|author=|date=2007-04-19|accessdate=2015-04-23|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304125001/http://game.21cn.com/comic/news/a/2007/0419/15/3188817.shtml|archivedate=2016-03-04}}</ref>在《[[漫友|漫友]]·动画100》上连载，且有番外篇《黑白无双PRO》<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ycwb.com/ycwb/2008-01/25/content_1770158.htm|title=漫画新贵韩露、于彦舒|language=zh-cn|publisher=金羊网|author=|date=2008-01-25|accessdate=2015-04-23|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080614233018/http://www.ycwb.com/ycwb/2008-01/25/content_1770158.htm|archivedate=2008-06-14}}</ref>。另有改编同名动画作品一、二季。
《黑白无常》是[[于彦舒|于彦舒]]在《[[漫友|漫友]]·动画100》连载的漫画，而作者自己也相信死后世界，也觉得那样合理。
